Bohdanowicz, 1987 (see 
<bibRefCitation id="55C8656170A385B86C99E6EAC96AB14F" author="Bohdanowicz, A" journalOrPublisher="Courier Forschungsinstitut Senckenberg" pageId="0" pageNumber="59" pagination="65 - 86" refId="B2" refString="Bohdanowicz, A, 1987. Salticidae from the Nepal Himalayas: The genus Synagelides Boesenberg &amp; Strand 1906. Courier Forschungsinstitut Senckenberg 93: 65 - 86" title="Salticidae from the Nepal Himalayas: The genus Synagelides Boesenberg &amp; Strand 1906." volume="93" year="1987">Bohdanowicz 1987</bibRefCitation>
